<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="fr">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>Merci pour votre commande !</title>
  <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Roboto:wght@400;700&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
  <style>
    body {
      font-family: 'Roboto', sans-serif;
      background-color: #f0f4f8;
      margin: 0;
      padding: 0;
      display: flex;
      justify-content: center;
      align-items: center;
      height: 100vh;
      text-align: center;
    }
    section {
      background-color: #ffffff;
      padding: 40px;
      border-radius: 10px;
      box-shadow: 0 4px 8px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
      width: 90%;
      max-width: 450px;
      animation: slideIn 0.5s ease-out forwards;
    }
    @keyframes slideIn {
      from {
        transform: translateY(20px);
        opacity: 0;
      }
      to {
        transform: translateY(0);
        opacity: 1;
      }
    }
    h1 {
      color: #333;
      margin-bottom: 24px;
    }
    p {
      color: #666;
      line-height: 1.6;
    }
    a {
      display: inline-block;
      padding: 12px 24px;
      margin-top: 24px;
      border-radius: 5px;
      background-color: #5cb85c;
      color: #ffffff;
      text-decoration: none;
      font-weight: bold;
      transition: background-color 0.3s;
    }
    a:hover {
      background-color: #4cae4c;
    }
    .icon {
      font-size: 48px;
      color: #5cb85c;
      margin-bottom: 24px;
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <section>
    <div class="icon">✔️</div>
    <h1>Merci pour votre commande !</h1>
    <p>Nous apprécions votre entreprise ! Si vous avez des questions, veuillez envoyer un email à <a href="mailto:innohire@esprit.tn">innohire@esprit.tn</a>.</p>
    <p>Montant rechargé : {{ montant }} DT</p>
    <a href="{{ path('app_etablissement_front') }}">Retour à l'accueil</a>
  </section>
</body>
</html>
